Package: pacerR
Type: Package
Title: Automated Retrieval and Network Analysis of PACER Court Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sacha", "Bechara", 
                  email = "sacha.bechara.23@ucl.ac.uk", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for authenticated access to the PACER (Public Access 
    to Court Electronic Records) system, automated retrieval of case dockets in XML 
    format, and discovery of associated case networks. Designed for academic and 
    computational legal research. Users are responsible for understanding PACER fees 
    and obtaining appropriate fee exemptions. This tool was developed for research 
    on litigation in US federal courts and includes responsible rate-limiting.
